'''苯甲腈'''是具有[[示性式|示性式]] C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>CN的[[芳香|芳香]][[化合物|化合物]]，简写为[[苯基|Ph]]CN。苯甲腈是一种無色，有甜杏仁味的液体。它可以通过[[苯甲酰胺|苯甲酰胺]]脱水或者通过[[氰化钠|氰化钠]]和[[溴苯|溴苯]]反应制备。

== 應用 ==
苯甲腈是一种有用的溶剂，可以做成許多衍生物。它和胺反应的生成物水解後可得到N－取代的苯甲酰胺。<ref>{{OrgSynth | author = Cooper, F.C.; Partridge, M. W. | title = N-Phenylbenzamidine | collvol = 4 | collvolpages = 769 | year = 1963 | prep = cv4p0769}}</ref>它是通过与苯基溴化镁反应再甲醇解制备Ph<sub>2</sub>C=NH（沸点151 °C，8mm Hg）的前体。<ref>{{OrgSynth | author = Pickard, P. L.; Tolbert, T. L. | title = Diphenyl Ketimine | collvol = 5 | collvolpages = 520 | year = 1973 | prep = cv5p0520}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
苯甲腈最早于1844年被德國化學家{{link-en|赫尔曼·斐林|Hermann Fehling}}发现，他利用加热苯甲酸铵，使其分解的方式得到。<ref>{{cite journal
 | journal = [[Annalen_der_Chemie_und_Pharmacie|Annalen der Chemie und Pharmacie]]
 | volume = 49
 | issue = 1
 | pages = 91–97
 | year = 1844
 | title = Ueber die Zersetzung des benzoësauren Ammoniaks durch die Wärme
 | author = Hermann Fehling
 | doi = 10.1002/jlac.18440490106 }}</ref>

2018年，苯甲腈被发现存在于[[星际物质|星际物质]]中。<ref name="SC-20180112">{{cite journal |title=Detection of the aromatic molecule benzonitrile (c\sC6H5CN) in the interstellar medium |journal=[[Science_(journal)|Science]] |first1=Brett A. |last1=McGuire |first2=Andrew M. |last2=Burkhardt |first3=Sergei |last3=Kalenskii |first4=Christopher N. |last4=Shingledecker |first5=Anthony J. |last5=Remijan |first6=Eric |last6=Herbst |first7=Michael C. |last7=McCarthy |display-authors=1 |volume=359 |issue=6372 |pages=202–205 |date=January 2018 |doi=10.1126/science.aao4890 |bibcode=2018Sci...359..202M |arxiv=1801.04228 |pmid=29326270}}</ref>

==危害==
燃烧苯甲腈会产生含有氢氰酸的气体。<ref name="GESTIS" />

